                     <interp inst="t18460511-1208-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp> stealing 19 live tame fowls the property of <persName id="t18460511-name-1159" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18460511-name-1159" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460511-name-1159" type="surname" value="LEESON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460511-name-1159" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18460511-1208-offence-1 t18460511-name-1159"></join>William Leeson</persName>; and that Johnson had been before convicted of felony.</rs>
